{"tid":1631951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[警世］大家仲記唔記得無分和勇","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:06.000Z","uid":143680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1b46d6dd2fcbb1e6550394e713996823a582df","tid":1631951,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"首先我想講句 <br />\n同行兒女 為正義時代革命 <br />\n我愛大家<br />\n<br />\n活動嚟到第四個月 <br />\n呢個月將會係我哋最艱辛嘅時候<br />\n大家仲記唔記得不分和勇？<br />\n最近多咗好多分化互相猜疑post <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先希望大家相信前線係有智慧</span></span><br />\n大家仲記唔記得7 1入立法會<br />\n大家仲記唔記得721係上環果晚<br />\n勇武所有行動都有背後原因<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">就好似前日咁</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">我仆街我唔明點解黃大仙勇武玩陣地</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">但之後有手足解釋返<br />\n原來佢哋係想塞死龍翔道停止黑警運backup</span> </span><br />\n<br />\n到今日好多人唔明點解要咁激烈私了的士司佬<br />\n喂大佬條仆街車斷人隻腳<br />\n依家黑警選擇性執法<br />\n別無他法下唯有私下解決<br />\n<br />\n至於裝修店舖方面<br />\n呢幾日先come up左黃黑紅藍分類<br />\n各位手足需要時間跟隨<br />\n希望大家唔好互相指責<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">和理非都會繼續做好<br />\n文宣<br />\n外國戰線宣傳<br />\n民眾號召力</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[orange]但有樣嘢好想手足可以做<br />\n當每次發生激烈衝突<br />\n玩陣地？任何攻略？<br />\n希望有手足可以同我地解釋返個原因<br />\n等文宣組可以同大眾解釋返<br />\n<br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: blue;\">大家切記無分和勇<br />\n兩者結合先係致勝之道<br />\n活動過後可以檢討<br />\n大家互相了解下<br />\n 再搵一個解決方案<br />\n而唔係互相指責</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbwwd0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcbwwd0U.png&h=da00cf50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9d6swNA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9d6swNA.png&h=98cf94eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後最後<br />\n為咗 犧牲左嘅烈士<br />\n我哋要努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bbkpy1Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbbkpy1Q.png&h=26478b39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2d9ca51ddfae556bc131c1069f35d5a62d38f48","tid":1631951,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c16ac871977805e0710d5f65e217dc25dee2d61b","tid":1631951,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ae439aebd20850c437cf5b393195f3052f30b16c","tid":1631951,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:39.000Z","msg":"大家不分和勇"},{"pid":"4453943a21601adc02b8c6ff9cfed2f65c0a2e7a","tid":1631951,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 不篤灰"},{"pid":"5625468c5f45d03d80398123e70ae1c6b8dd9873","tid":1631951,"uid":143680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"可賽後檢討"}]}